OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with patchy rain
OL,7,Fslowly easing away eastwards. Dry for
OL,8,Fmany overnight with clearing skies,
OL,9,Fespecially in the west. Turning chilly
OL,10,Funder the clear skies with perhaps
OL,11,Fsome mist and fog patches developing
OL,12,Fby dawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,15,Fspells, especially in the north.
OL,16,FSouthern areas seeing more in the way
OL,17,Fof cloud with the odd spot of rain
OL,18,Fpossible. Feeling fresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
