OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Ffine day on Wednesday, with sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Most likely dry on Thursday,
OL,8,Fbut rain possible by the evening. This
OL,9,Fclearing to leave another dry and
OL,10,Fsunny day on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
